# Generated chart variants — regenerate with scripts/plot_results.py.
# Only assets/results-graph.png (the canonical chart shown in README) is
# committed. Historical (--version) or extra-language (--extra) variants
# produce a suffixed filename and stay local.
assets/results-graph_*.png
assets/benchmark_*.png

# Talk-specific slide artefacts — regenerate with scripts/plot_slide.py.
# Script is committed; rendered PNGs are talk-prep ephemera and go into
# the speaker's slide deck rather than the repo.
assets/vera-bench_slide_*.png
